text: Georgia Southwestern State University (GSW) is a public university in Americus, Georgia. It is part of the University System of Georgia and offers bachelor's degree programs along with selected master's and specialist degree programs. ==References== Category:1900s establishments in Georgia (U.S. state) Category:1906 establishments in the United States Category:Colleges and universities in Georgia (U.S. state)
